   lustre-client-modules-&amp;lt;ver&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
in the manual, but &lt;br/&gt;
   kmod-lustre-client-2.9.0-1   ?&lt;br/&gt;
   lustre-client-dkms-2.9.0-1   ?&lt;br/&gt;
in the downloads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
